short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A Chrome extension to integrate with telematics provider vehicle and address data.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The NextBillion - TSP Integration extension allows users of the NextBillion Route Planner application to pull required data via an API interface from various telematics service provider platforms (assets/vehicles, addresses etc.) and format this data into a schema required by NextBillion. The formatted input is then copied to the user's clipboard for use in the planner.
